aviciFabricHardwareVersion.name: aviciFabricHardwareVersion
aviciFabricHardwareVersion.description: The current hardware version of the fabric.

aviciFabricRoutingProtocolVersion.name: aviciFabricRoutingProtocolVersion
aviciFabricRoutingProtocolVersion.description: The current fabric routing protocol version used on the fabric.

aviciFabricCountersTable.name: aviciFabricCountersTable

aviciFabricHiPriPktsInserted.name: aviciFabricHiPriPktsInserted
aviciFabricHiPriPktsInserted.description: High priority packets inserted into the fabric from an input framer and destined for some other module in the system.

aviciFabricLoPriPktsInserted.name: aviciFabricLoPriPktsInserted
aviciFabricLoPriPktsInserted.description: Low priority packets inserted into the fabric from an input framer and destined for some other module in the system.

aviciFabricHiPriPktsForwarded.name: aviciFabricHiPriPktsForwarded
aviciFabricHiPriPktsForwarded.description: High priority packets forwarded through this module.

aviciFabricLoPriPktsForwarded.name: aviciFabricLoPriPktsForwarded

aviciFabricHiPriFlitsForwarded.name: aviciFabricHiPriFlitsForwarded
aviciFabricHiPriFlitsForwarded.description: High priority flits (parts of packets) forwarded through this module.

aviciFabricLoPriFlitsForwarded.name: aviciFabricLoPriFlitsForwarded
aviciFabricLoPriFlitsForwarded.description: Low priority flits (parts of packets) forwarded through this module.

aviciFabricExtractedCountersTable.name: aviciFabricExtractedCountersTable
aviciFabricExtractedCountersTable.description: This table contains fabric extracted counters.

aviciFabricExtractedCountersEntry.name: aviciFabricExtractedCountersEntry
aviciFabricExtractedCountersEntry.description: An entry in the Avici Fabric Extracted Counters table.

aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPktsSelf.name: aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPktsSelf
aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPktsSelf.description: High priority packets extracted from the fabric whose destination is this module.

aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPktsSelf.name: aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPktsSelf
aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPktsSelf.description: Low priority packets extracted from the fabric whose destination is this module.

aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPkts.name: aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPkts
aviciFabricExtractedHiPriPkts.description: High priority packets extracted from the fabric whose destination is this module.

aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPkts.name: aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPkts
aviciFabricExtractedLoPriPkts.description: Low priority packets extracted from the fabric whose destination is this module.

aviciFabricExtractedHiPriFlits.name: aviciFabricExtractedHiPriFlits

aviciFabricExtractedLoPriFlits.name: aviciFabricExtractedLoPriFlits

aviciFabricLinkTable.name: aviciFabricLinkTable
aviciFabricLinkTable.description: This table contains information for a fabric link.

aviciFabricLinkEntry.name: aviciFabricLinkEntry
aviciFabricLinkEntry.description: An entry in the Avici Fabric Link table.

aviciFabricLinkIndex.name: aviciFabricLinkIndex
aviciFabricLinkIndex.description: The index of the fabric link.

aviciFabricLinkDescr.name: aviciFabricLinkDescr
aviciFabricLinkDescr.description: A string containing a description of the link. This string could contain name of the module at the other end of this link. Example: Plus X link to module 1/22

aviciFabricLinkAdminStatus.name: aviciFabricLinkAdminStatus
aviciFabricLinkAdminStatus.description: The current administrative state of the link.

aviciFabricLinkOperStatus.name: aviciFabricLinkOperStatus
aviciFabricLinkOperStatus.description: The current operational state of the link.

aviciFabricLinkSpeed.name: aviciFabricLinkSpeed
aviciFabricLinkSpeed.description: The speed of the fabric link in units of 1 Mb/s.

aviciFabricLinkCRCErrors.name: aviciFabricLinkCRCErrors
aviciFabricLinkCRCErrors.description: The number of CRC errors on the link.

aviciFabricLinkDownTransitions.name: aviciFabricLinkDownTransitions
aviciFabricLinkDownTransitions.description: The number of times this link has transitioned to the down state.

aviciFabricLinkLastChange.name: aviciFabricLinkLastChange
aviciFabricLinkLastChange.description: The time, in 1/00ths of a second, since this link last changed state.

aviciFabricChannelTable.name: aviciFabricChannelTable
aviciFabricChannelTable.description: This table contains information about fabric channels.

aviciFabricChannelEntry.name: aviciFabricChannelEntry
aviciFabricChannelEntry.description: An entry in the Avici Fabric Channel table.

aviciFabricChannelIndex.name: aviciFabricChannelIndex
aviciFabricChannelIndex.description: The index of the Fabric Channel pair. Each of the Fabric Channels consists of a high and a low priority channel.

aviciFabricChannelHiPriScrubEvents.name: aviciFabricChannelHiPriScrubEvents
aviciFabricChannelHiPriScrubEvents.description: The number of times the high priority Fabric Channel has scrubbed.

aviciFabricChannelLoPriScrubEvents.name: aviciFabricChannelLoPriScrubEvents
aviciFabricChannelLoPriScrubEvents.description: The number of times the low priority Fabric Channel has scrubbed.

aviciFabricChannelHiPriLastScrubTime.name: aviciFabricChannelHiPriLastScrubTime
aviciFabricChannelHiPriLastScrubTime.description: The time in 1/100ths of a second since the high priority Fabric Channel last scrubbed.

aviciFabricChannelLoPriLastScrubTime.name: aviciFabricChannelLoPriLastScrubTime
aviciFabricChannelLoPriLastScrubTime.description: The time in 1/100ths of a second since the low priority Fabric Channel last scrubbed.

aviciFabricLsaTable.name: aviciFabricLsaTable
aviciFabricLsaTable.description: This table contains Fabric Link State Advertisement database.

aviciFabricLsaEntry.name: aviciFabricLsaEntry
aviciFabricLsaEntry.description: An entry in the Avici Fabric Link State Advertisement table.

aviciFabricLsaOriginBay.name: aviciFabricLsaOriginBay
aviciFabricLsaOriginBay.description: The bay number for the module that originated this entry.

aviciFabricLsaOriginSlot.name: aviciFabricLsaOriginSlot
aviciFabricLsaOriginSlot.description: The slot number for the module that originated this entry.

aviciFabricLsaSequenceNum.name: aviciFabricLsaSequenceNum
aviciFabricLsaSequenceNum.description: The sequence number for this LSA. Sequence numbers start at 1 and are incremented by the originator every time the LSA is re-originated.

aviciFabricLsaCreationTime.name: aviciFabricLsaCreationTime
aviciFabricLsaCreationTime.description: A string containing the creation time for this LSA (wall clock time to 1/1000 sec).

aviciFabricLsaModuleReachable.name: aviciFabricLsaModuleReachable
aviciFabricLsaModuleReachable.description: True if the originator module is reachable from this module.

aviciFabricLsaChannels.name: aviciFabricLsaChannels
aviciFabricLsaChannels.description: The list of fabric channels currently assigned for this module. Example: 1 3 5 11

aviciFabricLsaModulePlusX.name: aviciFabricLsaModulePlusX
aviciFabricLsaModulePlusX.description: The immediate neighbor module on the plusX link.

aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusX.name: aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusX
aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusX.description: The immediate neighbor module on the minusX link.

aviciFabricLsaModulePlusY.name: aviciFabricLsaModulePlusY
aviciFabricLsaModulePlusY.description: The immediate neighbor module on the plusY link.

aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusY.name: aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusY
aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusY.description: The immediate neighbor module on the minusY link.

aviciFabricLsaModulePlusZ.name: aviciFabricLsaModulePlusZ
aviciFabricLsaModulePlusZ.description: The immediate neighbor module on the plusZ link.

aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusZ.name: aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusZ
aviciFabricLsaModuleMinusZ.description: The immediate neighbor module on the minusZ link.

aviciFabricLsaSummaryTable.name: aviciFabricLsaSummaryTable
aviciFabricLsaSummaryTable.description: This table contains summary information for the Fabric Link State Advertisement database.

aviciFabricLsaSummaryEntry.name: aviciFabricLsaSummaryEntry
aviciFabricLsaSummaryEntry.description: An entry in the LSA summary table.

aviciFabricLsaSummaryChecksum.name: aviciFabricLsaSummaryChecksum
aviciFabricLsaSummaryChecksum.description: The sum of all of the checksums of all LSA's in the LSA database on this module.

aviciFabricPathTable.name: aviciFabricPathTable
aviciFabricPathTable.description: This table contains information for a Fabric Routing Protocol link.

aviciFabricPathEntry.name: aviciFabricPathEntry
aviciFabricPathEntry.description: An entry in the Avici Fabric Routing Link State table.

aviciFabricPathIndex.name: aviciFabricPathIndex
aviciFabricPathIndex.description: The index for this fabric path.

aviciFabricPathDestinationBay.name: aviciFabricPathDestinationBay
aviciFabricPathDestinationBay.description: The destination bay for this fabric path.

aviciFabricPathDestinationSlot.name: aviciFabricPathDestinationSlot
aviciFabricPathDestinationSlot.description: The destination slot for this fabric path.

aviciFabricPathVector.name: aviciFabricPathVector
aviciFabricPathVector.description: The textual representation of the vector describing this fabric path. This vector is described using a shorthand notation for each fabric link from source to destination. Each component of the vector consists of: destination bay/slot fabricLink. Example: 1/1 +X 1/10 +Y 1/30 +Z 1/28 This example shows the path from module 1/1 to module 1/28. The first vector is the bay/slot of this module and the origin link onto the fabric. There are a maximum of 16 fabric hops in a path.
